1. WHAT MAKES REACT FAST ?

React has a concept of Virtual DOM
whenever anything is changed in a particular component that component changes. 
Now these changes are not pushed to the DOM directly, but instead it is pushed to something called VirtualDOM.
This is what makes it fast

2. What are React BENEFITS ?
Single Page Application.
Entire page remains same but only few components change.
Code is easy to scale and maintain.
More functionalities as HTML is created from JS
Isomorphic Rendering(Server side rendering)
Blazing speed
